data.description: Welcome to this beautiful property with a natural color palette throughout, creating a serene atmosphere and allowing for your personal touch. The kitchen boasts a nice backsplash, adding a touch of elegance to meal preparation, while other rooms provide flexible living space to suit your needs. The primary bathroom features good under sink storage, keeping your essentials organized and easily accessible. Outside, you'll find a tranquil sitting area in the backyard, perfect for unwinding after a long day. With fresh interior paint, this home is ready for you to make your mark. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity.This home has been virtually staged to illustrate its potential
